My name's Human Detective, I solve rodent-related cases, and you are?

Rat Sleuth, hm? Have you any proof that you're a real sleuth?

Too many poser sleuths nowadays. Show me something that can prove you're a real problem solver. I might even give you something cool as a reward.

(Loops last line until you USE sleuthing license on him.)

Nice sleuthing license, so here's a little gift from one detective to another. Hope you find it useful.

(Try TALKing to him after he gives you an item gives you this line.):

